\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{t\operatorname{sin}(\pi t)}{t^2+4}dt.
\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{t\operatorname{sin}(\pi t)}{t^2+4}dt=\frac{1}{2i}\left(\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{te^{i\pi t}}{t^2+4}dt-\int_{-\infty}^\infty \frac{te^{-i\pi t}}{t^2+4}dt\right).
